    "clusterId": "dfe0d881-e78b-4afb-8353-409e5d3b64dd",
    "text": "Carney's government believes India is not currently linked to violent crimes or threats on Canadian soil",
    "status": "disputed",
    "supportingSources": [
      "BBC World"
    ],
    "disputingSources": [
      "BBC World - citing Liberal MP from Carney's party and Sikh diaspora members"
